{"tid":502390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"拒唱中國國歌！舔共校長玻璃心爆發 轟畢業生出場","createTime":"2017-12-18T00:24:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-18T05:07:50.000Z","uid":53379,"like":6,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c0beb063e0e7c967d3d5bbf0f289f5c8fa8b954e","tid":502390,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T00:24:31.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">拒唱中國國歌！舔共校長玻璃心爆發 轟畢業生出場</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國全國人民代表大會常務委員會2017年11月5日修訂「國歌法」，該法尚未在香港上路，但香港一專校卻率先將其納入校規，釀畢業學生不滿，昨（16）日畢業典禮上拒絕肅立唱國歌，引發校長大罵學生「選錯校」。<br />\n<br />\n綜合港媒報導，香港專業進修學校2名社工系學生，不滿校方在「國歌法」落地香港前，率先訂定校規，要求學生在播放《義勇軍進行曲》時必須肅立與獻唱，因此於昨（16）日的畢業典禮上，拒絕在播放中國國歌時起立，並將雙手交叉於胸前，以示抗議。<br />\n<br />\n對此，校方立刻宣布，由於在場人士不尊重中國國歌，使畢業典禮無法莊嚴進行，因此宣布結束，抗議人士被校方請出場外後，畢業典禮還是繼續進行，校長陳卓禧事後至會場外，面對抗議學生，直呼「港專作為一個愛國愛港的學校，必定高舉愛國旗幟，這個是沒有任何妥協餘地的」、「你們如果連這件事都不知道，那就是你們選錯了學校」。<br />\n<br />\n即便學生強調，「唱國歌不代表愛國，不唱國歌不代表不愛國」，但校長依舊要求學生尊重校方立場。據悉，抗議學生是於頒授畢業證書前被請出場，除2名拒絕肅立學生外，亦有10餘名聲援學生一同離場。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpraUG9D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpraUG9D.jpg&h=8c81b4c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n即便學生強調，「唱國歌不代表愛國，不唱國歌不代表不愛國」，但校長依舊要求學生尊重校方立場。（圖擷取自影片）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2286070\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2286070&d=19uQxs6i8qeC%2B8O9irJc3y7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=65db9caf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2286070&h=a66de878\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2286070</a><br />\n<br />\n傳埋到去臺灣"},{"pid":"35e27a1fe02ff0a5b6c3e38b1061fe0471f60f3f","tid":502390,"uid":56999,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T00:29:16.000Z","msg":"條友精神有問題<br />\n<br />\n話英政府逼害佢<br />\n<br />\n係咪支那人都有被害妄想症"},{"pid":"b2d8a6d9b3d09563f02673e852b28893cbac99ab","tid":502390,"uid":85819,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T00:42:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fe791607444f9e18e85599492100f899b6a68c9c","tid":502390,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T01:44:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解教育局仲可以比呢d學校營運？長期收生不足？學校規模唔大？ 可以咁趕學校生完全個人意見。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n港共背景"},{"pid":"979a2db6d6e707aae29e1cd7a1bf8d53fa1afb31","tid":502390,"uid":73262,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T01:52:22.000Z","msg":"專重校方立場  咁邊個尊重學生立場呢"},{"pid":"1adcdbd9bb315f4d7d863a911f87a902028e4370","tid":502390,"uid":139766,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T02:00:56.000Z","msg":"無衝突㗎 <br />\n學校要你提前適應吓咁啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c582204822bfa848608441500e825493b5c81d5","tid":502390,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T02:07:35.000Z","msg":"依間垃圾學校<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4646b4b526eb00400b0422c6ab656432deb56c42","tid":502390,"uid":57513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T02:12:59.000Z","msg":"文革咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a10f532a3bdf444259e60212aebfd1ccc912eb6d","tid":502390,"uid":40052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T02:15:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>文革咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/as